{
  "text": "For real-time data analysis, the relative expression of the target gene in each sample was compared with the control sample (corresponding to control plants) and was determined with the delta-delta Ct method. The Ct for each sample was calculated using the Line-gene K software (fqdpcr ver. 4.2.00), where Ct refers to the threshold cycle determined for each gene in the exponential phase of PCR amplification. In this analysis method, the relative expression of the target gene in the control sample was equal to one (2 0 ) by definition [CITATION_1] .",
  "citation_candidates": [
